DOC.LD:
Congolese guerrillas captured a strategic eastern lakeside port
from government forces and their allies after a night of fierce fighting,
the rebels' commander said.

   Sheriff James Kugler, whose office wall is adorned with a life-size
poster of John Wayne, didn't pay much attention to the report either;
he's been busy investigating the county's first murder since 1941.
